Articles.Content:
• KSP version =1.1.01230 - Windows 10, 64-bit, and it's on Steam
  • i cant snap parts onto my command module,  i started doing the training missions but got stuck when i had to put a solid stage booster on, the snap point is in the center of the booster instead of the top so it snaps sideways, also i tried the intermediary construction mission and the de-coupler attaches ok but then the fuel tank wont snap , thanks for the help
  • screenshots = http://imgur.com/a/j6IWx
  • system specs - i5 - 3570l, 16gb ram, 250gb intel ssd,  msi gtx 660ti
  • unmodded game- fresh install and deleted all saves just in case
